relevant_findings.general: Well developed, well nourished in no acute distress.
relevant_findings.HEENT: Normocephalic, atraumatic, extraocular movements intact, anicteric.
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: Regular rate and rhythm, no jugular venous distention.
relevant_findings.abdominal: Soft, mild tenderness to palpation in right lower quadrant, non-distended, no mass or hernia, incisions clear, dry, intact.
relevant_findings.extremities: Warm, well perfused, no cyanosis, clubbing, or edema, 2+ bilateral radial pulses.
relevant_findings.neurological: Alert and oriented times three, no focal neurologic deficits.
relevant_findings.psychiatric: Normal judgment/insight, normal memory, normal mood/affect.
